      <title>萨巴在重组英国信托基金的行动中遭遇进一步失败</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/saba-suffers-second-defeat-campaign-shake-up-uk-trusts-2025-02-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，萨巴资本 (Saba Capital) 在重组英国 2690 亿英镑（3320 亿美元）投资信托行业的活动中遭遇进一步挫折，因为另外两个信托公司的股东拒绝了这位美国激进投资者的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/saba-suffers-second-defeat-campaign-shake-up-uk-trusts-2025-02-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
